    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather seats still retain their original scent and supple texture, free from any creases or wear. Every button, dial, and electronic feature functions with the precision of the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by certified specialists. With zero imperfections, no curb rash on the wheels, and a spotless undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
